Package jetbrains.mps.generator.impl

Class GenControllerContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • jetbrains.mps.generator.impl.GenControllerContext
  • public final class GenControllerContext
extends Object
    Holds parameters global for particular generation activity/task. Similar to GenerationSessionContext which is a context for per-model generation session, while this class tracks parameters that span generation of a single model. 'Context' is not the best pick, however, resemblance to GenerationSessionContext dictates its use.

    NOTE, this class is not a public API, it's 'public' in Java sense just to cross package boundaries
